          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "http://www.everydayaccountsblog.com/2016/02/travel-with-me-edinburgh/",
                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ],
            "text": "Edinburgh stay"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ", we decided to explore the Highlands with a tour company called "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "link",
                "attrs": {
                  "href": "https://www.rabbies.com/tour_scotland.asp",
                  "title": null
                }
              }
            ],
            "text": "Rabbie's"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " so that we could learn from a guide along the way and not have to worry about driving ourselves around. We picked the Loch Ness, Glencoe, and Highlands Day Tour, and it was exactly what we were hoping for."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
