            "type": "text",
            "text": "A full twelve hours after departure, we arrived back in Edinburgh sleepy but fully satisfied. A day in the Highlands is a gentle reminder that this world did not create itself but was handmade by our loving and powerful Creator. I am so thankful for this experience."
